<form class="well form-search">
  <div class="alert alert-block alert-error">
    <h4 class="alert-heading">查询数据失败情况!</h4>
    可以通过此页面查询个人提交的所有数据中后台因各种原因导致失败的情况，此数据状态只查询数据更新一次后的结果...
  </div>
  <label>指定输入需要查询的号码 : </label>
  <input type="text" class="input-medium search-query">
  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info">查 询 号 码</button>
</form>

<table class="table table-bordered ">
  <thead class="table-header-owen">
  <tr>
    <th colspan="5" style="text-align: center;">查询显示结果如下所示：</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>#序号</th>
    <th>停机号码</th>
    <th>后台状态</th>
    <th>下单人</th>
    <th>下单时间</th>
  </tr>
  </thead>
  <% @q_data.each_with_index do |x, index| %>
      <tr class="<%= cycle("list-line-odd", "list-line-even") %>">
        <td><%= index %></td>
        <td><%= x.sn %></td>
        <td><%= x.status %></td>
        <td><%= x.user.name %></td>
        <td class="span3"><%= x.created_at.strftime("%Y年-%m月%d日 %H:%M:%S") %></td>
      </tr>
  <% end %>
</table>
<div class="pagination pagination-small">
  <%= will_paginate @q_data %>
</div>
<div class="well">
  统计信息：共<%= @q_data.total_entries %>条,共<%= (@q_data.total_entries / @q_data.per_page)+1 %>页,
  当前第<%= @q_data.current_page %>页.
</div>

<div class="well">
